      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just... getting harder every day. i feel like i'm just a weight on everyone now. my daughter has to come over just to help me get dressed, and the kids are always worried about my appointments. i don't want to be a nuisance anymore. i think i've done my part, you know?",
